"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.2.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.2.6</span> 標題：嚼環和轡頭（bit and bridle）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מֶתֶג</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： metheg)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:3\">PRO 26:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:29\">ISA 37:29</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： רֶסֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： resen)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:5\">JOB 41:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:28\">ISA 30:28</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χαλινός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chalinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:3\">JAS 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:20\">REV 14:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χρυσοχάλινος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chrusochalinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:29\">2MA 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd3:6\">1ES 3:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κόσμος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kosmos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:3\">2MA 5:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σαγή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sagē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:25\">2MA 3:25</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0009_bronze_horse_bit.jpg\" alt=\"古代青銅馬銜\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">古代青銅馬銜 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>嚼環是一根短棍，通常由金屬製成，放在馬的嘴裡。短棍的兩端從馬嘴的兩側突出來，繫上繩索或皮帶，這些繩索或皮帶套在馬的頭部就成為轡頭。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0969_harness_bridle_hant.jpg\" alt=\"轡頭和嚼環\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">轡頭和嚼環 (© Gary Todd - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>騎馬者或車夫可以通過拉扯轡頭左側或右側的帶子來控制馬的行動。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0932_horse.jpg\" alt=\"馬和騎手展示韁繩的使用\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">馬和騎手展示韁繩的使用 (© Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>希伯來文<em>metheg</em> 和<em>resen</em> 分別指「嚼環」和「轡頭」（雖然<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:3\">PRO 26:3</a> 將<em>metheg</em> 譯為“bridle”「轡頭」）。希臘文<em>chalinos</em> 和<em>chrusochalinos</em> 既指嚼環也指轡頭。如果嚼環和轡頭等挽具在當地不為人所知，翻譯者可以使用描述性的短語，例如「引導馬匹的某物」或「放入馬嘴裡面以引導牠的某物」。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:20\">ZEC 14:20</a> 中，希伯來文<em>mtsilah</em> 可能是指馬的挽具上面會發出某種響聲的裝飾。在聖經中，這個詞只出現在這裡。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:20\">REV 14:20</a> 提到「馬的轡頭」（“a horse’s bridle”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）僅僅是用來指高度，即轡頭離地面的高度，因此我們可以將這個高度譯為「約一米半高」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> ）或「約五英呎高」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:29\">2MA 10:29</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd3:6\">1ES 3:6</a> 所用的希臘文詞語表明，轡頭的金屬件是由金子製成的。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
